Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.82,0:00:04.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.72,0:00:07.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字叫南千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.35,0:00:09.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,三姐妹的小妹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.04,0:00:13.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有时觉得姐姐有一个就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.55,0:00:14.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,无奈是三姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.55,0:00:24.81,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}今天全国以晴天为主…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.13,0:00:27.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  好好的吐我槽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.01,0:00:30.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,像是早已起床了啊什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.22,0:00:32.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在被炉里睡觉会感冒的哟什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.49,0:00:33.32,zhushi2,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  这就是二女儿夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.88,0:00:37.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,人如其名  如夏日阳光一样让人厌烦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.56,0:00:40.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么能引以为傲的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.75,0:00:43.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会是在想些什么失礼的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.10,0:00:45.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没在想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.65,0:00:48.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是觉得「夏奈今天也好精神啊」而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.86,0:00:50.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊  那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.26,0:00:52.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来换衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.90,0:00:58.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,暖暖的暖暖的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.46,0:01:02.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你这种依赖被炉的生活打算持续到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.54,0:01:04.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已经春天了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.23,0:01:08.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有被炉却不用  对它可是很失礼的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.42,0:01:10.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夏奈  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.63,0:01:12.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是女神吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.57,0:01:14.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,准备好的话  来吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.72,0:01:17.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,搞错了  这位是大女儿春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.14,0:01:21.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,人如其名  如春日阳光一样温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.32,0:01:22.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是引以为傲的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.70,0:01:23.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.92,0:01:24.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一二
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.01,0:01:25.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.08,0:01:28.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么也不能在被炉里换衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.15,0:01:31.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,春香姐姐也请说说她
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.34,0:01:36.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,春香姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.90,0:01:39.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,春香的外套再放里面暖暖么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.21,0:01:39.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.97,0:01:46.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千秋的制服已经暖好了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.97,0:01:49.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.31,0:01:52.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.84,0:01:56.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙打算依赖被炉生活到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.01,0:01:58.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已经春天了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.25,0:02:02.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有被炉却不用  对它可是很失礼的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.24,0:02:06.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  快点换好衣服来吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.84,0:02:11.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.37,0:00:01.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.79,0:03:48.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  今天也要精精神神地去上学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.70,0:03:49.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.03,0:03:52.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天会返还试卷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.81,0:03:56.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,疼疼疼  肚子疼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.68,0:03:58.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不休息可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.14,0:04:01.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以不要管我了你们先走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.50,0:04:03.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,考试成绩要给我看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.40,0:04:07.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.74,0:04:12.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算今天休息考试成绩也不会变  蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.17,0:04:16.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,出门喽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.50,0:00:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.67,0:04:17.65,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(800,300)}春天的开始、南家的开始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.50,0:00:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.83,0:04:25.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  还是那么充满人情味的绝妙分数
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.98,0:04:28.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但可能不会令春香满意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.12,0:04:31.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下回考试不扭转现状就不妙了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.01,0:04:33.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.60,0:04:35.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  找人教我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.30,0:04:37.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,圭子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.10,0:04:38.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.60,0:04:40.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,教我功课
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.14,0:04:44.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要  夏奈不会认真学的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.66,0:04:46.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的我可不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.65,0:04:49.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看好了我这认真的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.83,0:04:53.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思  现在没戴眼镜看不清
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.69,0:04:57.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  好奇怪  刚才还戴着的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.06,0:05:00.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,圭子没有回应我的请求
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.82,0:05:02.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.36,0:05:08.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,春香  去海边吧去海边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.78,0:05:11.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千秋想去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.01,0:05:13.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.39,0:05:15.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好  那么一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.97,0:05:21.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请求别人的时候  比起认真来纯真才更重要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.29,0:05:25.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,美雪  美雪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.78,0:05:28.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.64,0:05:32.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,身高和我家的千秋差不多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.84,0:05:33.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.20,0:05:37.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  纯朴的眼神很不错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.18,0:05:38.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.50,0:05:39.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,美雪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.75,0:05:41.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,突然这么说虽然很失礼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.04,0:05:44.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你成绩不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.50,0:05:46.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这么突然也太失礼了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.12,0:05:49.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我有一个让你提高成绩的好提议
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.73,0:05:50.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.87,0:05:54.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,圭子  教美雪功课吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.93,0:05:56.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来我家教就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.02,0:06:00.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,圭子  拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.10,0:06:05.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,美雪这么说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.05,0:06:06.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,成了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.16,0:06:08.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.74,0:06:10.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很好很好很棒哟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.47,0:06:12.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是我看上的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.47,0:06:18.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,搞不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.74,0:06:20.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,圭子  这里教我下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.60,0:06:22.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你自己稍微动动脑筋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.22,0:06:25.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,圭子  这里教我下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.68,0:06:26.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.21,0:06:28.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.36,0:06:30.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里这样做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.58,0:06:31.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.08,0:06:33.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,偏心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.20,0:06:35.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么光偏袒美雪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.63,0:06:38.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是为了教美雪的功课才来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.79,0:06:41.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夏奈  不要那么生气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.37,0:06:42.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.91,0:06:43.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.11,0:06:46.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,通过拜托别人得到想要的只适用于小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.88,0:06:51.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,靠自己的力量去达成目的这才是学习啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.51,0:06:58.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正如夏奈所说的我要靠自己的力量努力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.74,0:07:00.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这个气势  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.59,0:07:02.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.34,0:07:04.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.28,0:07:09.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.03,0:07:14.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,唔  降了一分
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.13,0:07:18.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然光靠一个人的力量是不行的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.58,0:07:21.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,人类不互相帮助是不行的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.93,0:07:22.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.90,0:07:23.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.84,0:07:26.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏了夏奈  我第一次得了100分
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.48,0:07:28.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要去做就能成功的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.42,0:07:30.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来  夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.96,0:07:33.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我长高的方法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.14,0:07:35.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可以  不过要教我功课
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.78,0:07:37.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,人类要互相帮助才行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.50,0:00:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.47,0:07:40.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,圭子  教我功课
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.79,0:07:41.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,才不要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.16,0:07:42.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.37,0:07:44.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,南家三姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.50,0:00:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
